  <p>(d) &ldquo;<b>Buyer</b>&rdquo; means an end user on the Assignment Platform that wishes to enter into an assignment transaction to assume all obligations, rights and interests under an APS (including, the interests to the Property described therein) from a prospective seller.</p>
