  <p>(a) qualified Sellers may submit a listing of their Property (in which they have an interest) on the Assignment Platform for the purpose of marketing that such Property is make generally available to the public for assignment (each, an &ldquo;<b>Assignment Listing</b>&rdquo;) in accordance with the terms and conditions set out in Section 3 of this Exhibit A;</p>
